            <title>[LU-9895] How to Write to Lustre File System from Lustre Client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9895</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have Installed the Lustre Client on RHEL 7.3 by using the &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Intel+Cloud+Edition+for+Lustre+software+-+Client+Setup&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Intel+Cloud+Edition+for+Lustre+software+-+Client+Setup&lt;/a&gt; Website. Lustre Client Installed Sucessfully. We have to connect Lustre Client to Lustre File System. We googled but not able to find the proper Solution for that . If you can help then it would be great and appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
